primary.context: Caller wanted to know how to handle their rental agreement
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and offered to send a link to complete the rental agreement online.

steps: Caller asked about rental agreement instructions.
Agent performed account lookup and verified identity (name spelling and state).
Agent explained the purpose of the rental agreement.
Agent offered to send a link via email and text.
Caller accepted and confirmed no further needs.

clarifications.note: Agent asked to spell name for verification

actions.detail: Prepared rental agreement link for delivery

insights.summary: The caller wanted instructions on how to submit a rental agreement. The AI successfully verified the account and sent a link to complete the process online.
insights.verbatim: What do I do with the rental agreement?
